<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Rescheduled</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4a89dc;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .appointment-details {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #4a89dc;
        }
        .old {
            text-decoration: line-through;
            color: #888;
        }
        .new {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4a89dc;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4a89dc;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Appointment Rescheduled</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Dear {{ recipientName }},</p>
        
        <p>Your appointment with Dr. {{ doctorName }} has been rescheduled .</p>
        
        <div class="appointment-details">
            <p><span class="old">Original Date: {{ originalDate }}</span><br>
            <span class="new">New Date: {{ newDate }}</span></p>
            
            <p><span class="old">Original Time: {{ originalTime }}</span><br>
            <span class="new">New Time: {{ newTime }}</span></p>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need to make further changes, please contact our office.</p>
        
        <p>
            <a href="{{ appointmentLink }}" class="btn">View Appointment Details</a>
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from Medical Clinic.</p>
        <p>&copy; {{ currentDate|date('Y') }} Medical Clinic. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>